<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='4728:4751'>祭天地以䟽布巾幂八尊後鄭注幂人云以巾覆物曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='4751:4774'>幂天地之神尚質故用䟽布巾也賈義云天地無祼唯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='4774:4797'>有五齊三酒實於八尊此據正尊而言若五齊加明水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='4797:4821'>三酒加𤣥酒則十六尊皆以䟽布幂之天地雖無鬱鬯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='4821:4844'>之彞亦用䟽布幂之其四望山川社稷林澤亦用䟽布</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='4844:4867'>是尚質也此巾亦用二尺二寸之幅而圎也禮幂巾有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='4867:4890'>用絺綌者至於帨巾亦用布今唐禮亦用布或羅絹而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='4890:4893'>已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='4893:4920'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '014-24a' );" name="014-24a" class="pb">[014-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
